<?php

$local_file_paths = getenv('LocalFilePaths');
$local_file_paths_arr = explode("\t",$local_file_paths);
$fput_file_paths_arr = array();

foreach ($local_file_paths_arr as $file_path) {
    $file_path_q = '"'.$file_path.'"';
    $path_type_info = `file -b $file_path_q`;
    if (trim($path_type_info) != "directory") {
        array_push($fput_file_paths_arr,$file_path);
    }
}

$fput_count = count($fput_file_paths_arr);
if ($fput_count == 0) {
    echo "none";
} elseif ($fput_count == 1) {
    echo "single";
} else {
    echo "multiple";
}

?>

<?php


$key_str = `cat ~/.qshell/account.json`;
$key_arr = json_decode($key_str,true);

$AccessKey = $key_arr["access_key"];
$SecretKey = $key_arr["secret_key"];

$output = '{"items": [
	{
		"title": "AccessKey",
		"subtitle": "'.$AccessKey.'【回车复制，⌘+回车显示】'.'",
		"arg": "'.$AccessKey.'"
	},
	{
		"title": "SecretKey",
		"subtitle": "'.$SecretKey.'【回车复制，⌘+回车显示】'.'",
		"arg": "'.$SecretKey.'"
	}
]}';


echo $output;


?>
